flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Real-time production data availability and periodic KPI review cycles.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect real-time production data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: UI Screens - Generate KPI dashboards]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Forecast equipment failures and quality issues]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: AutoML - Analyze cost-of-quality]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Digital Twin - Simulate process changes]
  N5 --> N6{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Prioritize continuous improvement projects}
  N6 -->|Primary| P1[Action: Surface real-time production data and respond to anomalies.]
  P1 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved EBITDA, strengthened working capital, optimized line sequencing, and enhanced OTIF-enabled production planning.]
  N6 -->|Anomaly detected in real-time data| B1[Alert and initiate immediate corrective action]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Minimized downtime]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Significant deviation in KPIs| B2[Generate alerts and recommend corrective actions]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Optimized working capital]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|High probability of equipment failure| B3[Schedule preventive maintenance]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Reduced COGS]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]